Hi, on a call with a customer who asked the following, could someone please help me with the answers?
• Have we fine tuned any of the models at all - I think the answer here is no?
• Are we using the same hyperparams and temperatures for the GPT 3.5 and 4 models?
The questions came from them not understanding why GPT 4 would give better results thats GPT 3.
